dataIdInfo.idPurp: This shapefile represents the current stock boundary for pantropical spotted dolphins around Oahu in the main Hawaiian Islands.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: This shapefile represents the current stock boundary for pantropical spotted dolphins around Oahu in the main Hawaiian Islands. This boundary is based on biological data that have suggested that spotted dolphins within this boundary are demographically independent. More information on this boundary and other spotted dolphin stocks can be found in the latest stock assessment report.
dataIdInfo.idCredit: This shapefile was created from archived point data by Amanda Bradford <amanda.bradford@noaa.gov> at the NOAA Fisheries Pacific Islands Fisheries Science Center. The current projection is WGS_1984_UTM_Zone_4N.
